snippet: Henrik Stenson closed in on the European Tour money title, making birdies on four of his last five holes for a 5-under-par 67 and a one-shot lead at the World Tour Championship.
abstract: Henrik Stenson closes in on the European Tour money title, with one-shot lead after three rounds of the season-ending World Tour Championship in Dubai, United Arab Emirates; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Henrik Stenson closed in on the European Tour money title, making birdies on four of his last five holes for a 5-under-par 67 and a one-shot lead at the World Tour Championship.
